snippet.title: The Kostka - Announcement
snippet.description:
Yaay our first ever commercial game is coming.
Steam: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1627770
Xbox: https://www.microsoft.com/store/apps/9P2K8Q17PPZL
Playstation: https://store.playstation.com/en-cz/concept/10003141/

The Kostka is a mind boggling explorative voxel adventure featuring two main characters who just wanna get to the end.
